@host = https://localhost:7180
@orderId = 52787489-bf83-417b-859f-9d0d9f2c25f3

### Create an order
POST {{host}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: cache-demo-001

{
  "customerId": "f6e92b94-4967-4e5c-b78f-734f88d8673d",
  "lines": [
    { "sku": "COURSE-001", "quantity": 2 }
  ]
}

### Read order - first call loads from database
GET {{host}}/orders/{{orderId}}

### Read order - second call should hit HybridCache
GET {{host}}/orders/{{orderId}}

### Expensive summary - first call computes
GET {{host}}/orders/{{orderId}}/summary

### Expensive summary - subsequent call should use cache
GET {{host}}/orders/{{orderId}}/summary

### Output cached summary
GET {{host}}/orders/{{orderId}}/summary-output

### Invalidate order and summary cache
POST {{host}}/orders/{{orderId}}/refresh-cache